<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrīśakavaruṣaṁbulu 1154 gunē
<lb n="2" break="no"/><unclear>ṇṭi</unclear> kanyābrihaspati saṁvatsaramuna mēṣasa
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṁkrāṁtti nimittaṁbuna śrīcaturddaśa bhuvanā
<lb n="4" break="no"/>dhīśvarulaina vijayuvāḍa śrīmallēśvaraśrī
<lb n="5" break="no"/>mahādēvaraku Ācaṁdrārkkasthāyigā nakhaṁ
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ḍadīpamunaku sakalaśivabhaktavatsaluṁ
<lb n="7"/>ḍaina <unclear>śi</unclear>vayōgi mādayadēvaralu <unclear>ni</unclear>
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṁdrakīlaparvvatamunaṁdu Anna muḍigi tapassē
<lb n="9" break="no"/>yucu nuṁḍi dēvidēvaruvivāhamu sēsi tama <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="10"/>ṭṭijēgaṁṭadhāralasahitamu dīpānaku niccina mōdālu 25 <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
<lb n="11"/>vīniṁ jēkoni salle nūṁkanabōyini koḍku <unclear>ma</unclear>
<lb n="12" break="no"/>llebōyuṁḍu tana putrānupau(vu)trikamu
<lb n="13" break="no"/>na nitya māneṁḍu neyi naḍapaṁgalavāru <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
</p>

